:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">收单机构将</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">根据您的指令对您的银行卡进行扣款；</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;">B</span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">、交易查询：本公司将对您使用</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">博思致新</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">服务的操作的全部或部分进行记录，不论该操作之目的最终是否实现。您可以登录</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">博思致新账号</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">查询您</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">博思致新账号</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">的交易记录；</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;">C</span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">、其他，包括但不限于以上内容。</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">您授权并同意，</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">博思致新</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">有权根据您向</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">博思致新</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">发送的交易指令</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">转发至收单机构，由收单机构</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">划转您银行账户的资金到其他银行账户，并且确保已与您的开户银行签订的相关协议中包含了该授权。</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">（</font>2）如果您尚未注册成为本服务之用户，当他人通过本服务向您支付款项时，本公司将无法替您接收此笔款项，直到您成功注册成为本服务之用户，并指示本公司您愿意收取该笔款项时，本公司才能根据本公司的流程规定和要求替您接受此笔款项。</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><br></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">	</span><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">（</font>3）任何情况下，您的资金将始终独立于本公司</span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">自有</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">资金之外，本公司不会将您的资金用于非您指示的用途上</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">，也不会触碰您的资金</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">。</font></span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">（四）本服务使用条款</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><br></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;">1、信用卡及网上银行使用之确认：本服务所有的使用者在使用信用卡及银行账户交易前，需首先确定该信用卡已经发卡银行确认为有效卡，且该银行账户亦经确认为有效账户。信用卡使用需遵守相关法律法规及中国人民银行及各商业银行相关规定，不得使用信用卡恶意套取现金。</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">2</span><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">、交易笔数和交易额度限制：按照目前中国人民银行监管要求，根据您的身份信息认证程度不同，对于您在</font></span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">支付机构</font></span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">开立的支付账户，可分为</font>Ⅰ类、Ⅱ类、Ⅲ类支付账户，不同账户享有不同的账户余额支付额度限制。对于Ⅰ类支付账户，余额付款交易自账户开立起累计不超过1000元（包括支付账户向您本人同名银行账户转账）；对于Ⅱ类支付账户，所有支付账户的余额付款交易年累计不超过10万元（不包括支付账户向您本人同名银行账户转账）；对于Ⅲ类支付账户，所有支付账户的余额付款交易年累计不超过20万元（不包括支付账户向您本人同名银行账户转账）。此外，本公司拥有调整本服务之注册用户交易笔数（日、月、年交易笔数）和交易额度（单笔及日、月、年交易额度）的权利。具体交易笔数和交易额度限制以本公司通过</span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">博思致新官网</font></span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">（</font></span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">www.bosssoft.com.cn</span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">）、</font></span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">博思致新平台</font></span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">发布的移动客户端应用程序或其他方式给出的通知、交易规则等并经您通过相关页面确认已接收完整信息后为准。</font></span></u></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">3、交易退回：当您使用本服务进行付款时，可能由于</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">清算机构</font></span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size: