 SC">，</font></span></b><b><u><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">调整的手续费自公告届满</font>30日</span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">并经您通过相关页面确认已接收完整信息后</font></span></u></b><b><u><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">起生效</font></span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">。如您不同意调整内容的，应立即停止使用本服务，否则视为您已接受调整内容。除非另有说明或约定，您同意本公司有权自您委托本公司代收或代付的款项或者其他资产中直接扣除上述服务费用。</font></span></u></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;">8、电子联系：您同意本公司使用电子方式与您保持联系。电子方式包括发送电子邮件、将需告知您的信息公布于</span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">博思致新官网</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">（</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;">www.bosssoft.com.cn</span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">）上、或使用移动通讯装置。</font></span></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">如果您不同意以电子方式联系，本公司拥有结束您使用本服务的权利。</font></span></u></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">9、连线设备：为使用本服务，您应当使用具备良好品质的连线设备。</span><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">若因您的连线设备损坏或故障，造成您与本服务连接时所进行的交易失败的，本公司将不承担您因此遭受的任何损失。</font></span></u></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;">10、行为限制：当您使用本服务时，严禁从事以下行为：</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">（</font>1）从事伪造、偷窃物品之交易；</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">（</font>2）从事任何与赌博性商品或行为有关之交易；</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">（</font>3）侵害第三者之知识产权或商业机密之交易；</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">（</font>4）从事欺诈、洗钱、恐怖融资等活动；</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">（</font>5）从事其他任何违反中华人民共和国法律法规或政策规定的不正当交易。</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;">11、</span></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">客户责任：若您发现任何未经许可的交易，或者有人已经知悉您的</font></span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">博思致新账号</font></span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">密码或</font></span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">博思致新账号</font></span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">，或者您发现您的交易和提现记录有误，或者您的</font></span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">博思致新账号</font></span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">存在其他安全问题，您必须立即通知本公司，这是您的义务和责任。</font></span></u></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">12、如果您发现有未经您授权产生的交易或资金提现，您必须立刻通知本公司，这是您的义务和责任。您的及时通知将可能有助于保护您的权益。</span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><br></span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">13、您同意本公司有权基于单方判断，包含但不限于本公司认为您已经违反本服务条款的明文规定及精神，或在发现异常交易或有疑异或有违法之虞时不经事先通知而</span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">由收单机构</font></span></u></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">冻结您的账号、密码，对账户中的余额资金进行冻结，并拒绝您使用本服务之部分或全部功能。您在希望将您在账户中的款项恢复正常时，本公司有权要求您向本公司提供合法有效的交易证据，必要时您应就您提供的证据向本公司、银行或有关司法机构予以说明。否则，您应独立承担由此造成的一切损失。</font></span></u></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;">14、</span><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">在发生任何违法交易、盗窃或诈骗行为或洗钱、恐怖融资等触犯刑法之情况时，本公司将有权：（</font>1）暂停服务；（2）</span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">通知收单机构或有权机构</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">冻结账户余额资金</font>&nbsp;<font face="PingFang SC">；（</font>3）要求您及时提供所有的交易材料证明；（4）并有权向有关监管机构或司法机关报告，按照有关司法机关之指示行事。</span></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">由此造成账户冻结或款项转移而涉及您的合法权益时，您应及时主动向本公司、银行或有关司法机构提供有关交易证据，必要时您应就您提供的证据向银行或有关司法机构进行说明，如未能提供真实有效的交易证据，您应独立承担由此造成的一切损失。因您的行为造成本公司损失的，由您承担赔偿责任。</font></span></u></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;">15、本公司保留对可疑交易、非法交易、高风险交易或交易纠纷的独立判断和确定，并按以下情况进行处理：（1）如果本公司发现您涉及可疑交易、非法交易、高风险交易或交易纠纷的</span></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">，本公司有权向有关单位报告，并要求您及时提供所有的交易材料证明；（</font>2）本公司可视情况暂停相应服务</span></u></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">；（</font>3）如遇有关单位的合法指示（包括查询、冻结、扣划、解冻等），</span></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">本公司将依有关单位的指示行事。</font></span></u></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;">16、证据保留：您支付账户或银行</span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">账号</font></span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">资金余额被冻结时，为使您的利益得到有效的保护，您需保留与实际交易有关的一切证据。这些证据至少应包括订单号、交易双方姓名、交易日期、交易金额、交易商品或服务内容、收货地址、发货单、运输</font>/邮寄单据、收货人签收单及数字产品E-MAIL签收回复等。有关交易信息应保留至少18个月，法律法规另有规定的除外。</span></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;">17、</span></b><b><u><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;text-decoration:underline;text-underline:single;font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">因以下情况本公司没有成功完成您发出的电子支付指令，本公司不承担责任，但应当及时向您发出反馈：</font></span></u></b><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-weight:bold;font-size:14.0000pt;"><font face="PingFang SC">（</font>1）本公司接收到的支付指令信息不明、存在乱码、不完整等情形；（2）您的银行卡余额不足或信用额度不足；（3）您的银行卡状态不正常，致使无法完成支付；（4）其他不可抗力或其他不可归责于本公司的事由致使本公司不能正确执行您的支付指令。</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';color:rgb(0,0,0);font-size:14.0000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p" style="text-indent:21.0000pt;mso-pagination:widow-orphan;"><b><span class="16" style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:'PingFang SC';co